Envirofacts,is,a,service,of,the,U,S,Environmental,Protection,Agency,It,provides,search,access,to,multiple,environmental,databases,which,may,include,data,on,such,things,as,toxic,chemical,releases,water,discharge,permit,compliance,hazardous,waste,handling,processes,Superfund,status,and,air,emission,estimates,among,others,The,Envirofacts,API,uses,the,REST,and,SOAP,protocols,and,returns,responses,in,XML,CSV,and,Excel,formats